            "notes": "Winota, Joiner of Forces is a powerful aggro commander that focuses on cheating creatures into play and overwhelming the opponent with a fast and aggressive strategy. The deck is packed with low-cost creatures and token generators to trigger Winota's ability, allowing you to put powerful creatures into play for free. By deploying creatures quickly and efficiently, you can apply pressure early in the game and maintain a strong board presence. The deck also includes combat tricks and protection spells to protect your creatures and disrupt your opponent's strategy. With Winota at the helm, the goal is to quickly build a commanding board state and push for victory before the opponent has a chance to stabilize."
